OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Frather cloudy overnight, but with a
OL,7,Ffew breaks in the cloud here and
OL,8,Fthere. Further showery outbreaks or
OL,9,Frain are possible at times, especially
OL,10,Fover higher ground.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy start with patchy
OL,13,Frain or drizzle. However the cloud
OL,14,Fwill lift and break up in places to
OL,15,Fallow some bright spells, before wet
OL,16,Fand windy weather arrives later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
