OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FIncreasingly changeable from
OL,7,FWednesday, with showers or longer
OL,8,Fspells of rain. Some sunny spells are
OL,9,Falso likely, with temperatures near
OL,10,Fnormal, but turning colder by Friday.
OL,11,FWindy at times.
